          "explanation": "A Brønsted-Lowry acid is a proton ($\\text{H}^+$) donor."
        },
        {
          "step": "Define Brønsted-Lowry base",
          "explanation": "A Brønsted-Lowry base is a proton ($\\text{H}^+$) acceptor."
        }
      ],
      "final_answer": "Acid: proton donor; Base: proton acceptor."
